 GENERAL:

   ESC             exit help / menus
   ALT + ENTER       toggle fullscreen (or double-click)
   ALT + SHIFT       toggle multiple monitor stretch

 PRESETS:

   SPACE / H       soft / hard cut to next preset
   BACKSPACE       go back to previous preset
   ` / ~           [un]lock current preset
   R               toggle random/sequential preset order 
   L               load specific preset
   M               show/hide preset-editing Menu
   S               save new preset
   A               do random mini-mash-up
   D               toggle warp & comp shader locks
   SHIFT + !       randomize warp shader
   SHIFT + @       randomize comp shader

 INFO:

   F1   help
   F4   show preset info
   F5   show fps
   F6   show rating
   
 HOTKEYS:

   F3   toggle fps to 30/60/90/120/144/240/360/unlimited
   F7   always on top
   F10  freeze/unfreeze screen (only on windowed)
   N    show per-frame monitor
